Chongqing secondary schools pilot modern apprenticeship system, the entrance is the enterprise prospective employees - Xinhua yesterday, the reporter learned from the Municipal Education Commission, from this year, the city will be in 60 secondary schools pilot "modern apprenticeship" talent training model, accept the pilot training of students at the same time with apprenticeship status, enrollment will be the pilot enterprise pre-recorded as a unit of employees. Municipal Education Commission requirements, standardize the admission of secondary schools and enterprise employment procedures, clear apprentices of secondary school students and enterprise employees, in accordance with the principle of two-way choice, apprentices, schools and enterprises to sign a tripartite agreement, for the apprentices aged 16 to 18 years old, must be signed by the apprentice, guardians, schools and enterprises four-party agreement to determine the rights and interests of all parties and apprentices in the training of specific positions, the Teaching content, rights and interests, etc. Encourage pilot schools to use modern apprenticeship form and cooperation with enterprises to jointly carry out enterprise staff pre-job training and transfer training. Pilot schools to reform the talent training model. The university and enterprises jointly design the talent training program, jointly develop professional teaching standards, curriculum standards, job standards, enterprise master standards, quality control standards and the corresponding implementation plan. Pilot to train the academic system for a pilot cycle, students in the enterprise internship time according to the professional talent training program to determine, the top internship is generally 6 months. Practice in enterprises should be implemented in the enterprise team-based management model, according to the characteristics of different professions, 1 master can take 2 to 5 apprentices to form a learning team to ensure that students are proficient in the skills required for each rotational training position. According to the arrangement, from 2016 to August 2019, the city in three batches to determine 60 municipal secondary modern apprenticeship pilot, the number of each pilot in about 50 people, a total of about 3,000 students (apprentices ) . In accordance with the principle of piloting and then implementing, gradually promoting from point to point, exploring the establishment of joint school-enterprise enrollment, joint training, integrated education of long-term mechanism, and effectively enhance the students' job skills, improve the students' employment rate and employment quality.
